mwbzutils (0.1.1~wmf-1+stretch) stretch-wikimedia; urgency=medium

  * appendbz2 new util to create appndable bz2 content
  * showcrcs new util to show bz2 file block crcs
  * show_byte_aligned_crcs.py new script to show byte aligned bz2 file
    block crcs
  * split_bz2.py new script to split a bz2 file into parts by page range
  * munge_crc_info.py new script to reformat showcrcs output and display
    combined crcs
  * basic tests for all C utils
  * bug fixes for dumpbz2filefromoffset, writeuptopageid

 -- Ariel T. Glenn <ariel@wikimedia.org>  Fri, 27 Nov 2020 11:46:10 +0200

